  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Mobility)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mas, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You do not provoke attacks of opportunity for moving, and gain a +4 bonus to Defense and saves against any traps you might trigger while moving.<br><br>Avoiding an Attack (1/day): Minimum perform DC 17. If you succeed, you may move up to 15 ft, as above (without the 10 ft rule). Using the technique this way costs 2 Chakra. You can use this technique to avoid an attack against a source with a CR of up to 1.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step allows you to use the technique to avoid an attack an additional time per day. Each step also increases the CR which you can avoid, at an increased Chakra cost.<br><br>The first step: CR 5.<br><br>The second step: Cost 3, CR 10. The third step: Cost 4, CR 15. The fourth step Cost 5, CR 20. The fifth step: Cost 6, CR 25.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
